{
  "texts": [
    "We have also discovered that choosing the best hyperparameters for deep learning models is a time-consuming process.",
    "Inadequately configured hyperparameters might have an impact on performance.",
    "Named Entity Recognition (NER) is very difficult and interesting topic in the area of research and development of Natural language processing (NLP).",
    "There are many problems due to the wide range of linguistic and script differences across Indian languages as well as the lack of annotated data.",
    "Although recent developments in active learning, cross-lingual transfer learning (TL) community-driven efforts and rule-based system have showed promise in addressing these difficulties."
  ]
}